00:40:20,080 --> 00:40:21,640
In the workforce,

661
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,760
every one of us is a rookie.

662
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:24,880
Like I said,

663
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:27,400
the New Energy Department
