687
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:41,040
You startled me!

688
00:41:42,240 --> 00:41:43,160
What's on your mind?

689
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:45,200
Just now,

690
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:48,440
Mr. Xu asked us to join him
