691
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,320
Did you agree to it?

692
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,320
No.

693
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,960
I said that I'll think it over.

694
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:57,600
Why are you so upset?

695
00:41:58,160 --> 00:42:01,120
